    "problemNumber": 24,
    "category": "Geometry",
    "subcategory": "Area",
    "difficulty": 5,
    "statement": "In the figure, ABCD is a rectangle and EFGH is a parallelogram. Using the measurements given in the figure, what is the length d of the segment that is perpendicular to HE and FG?",
